org.gcn.plinguacore.util.psystem.factory

Interface IPsystemFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCellLikePsystemFactory, AbstractPsystemFactory, CreationPsystemFactory, DivisionPsystemFactory, EvolutionCommunicationPsystemFactory, EvSymportAntiportPsystemFactory, ProbabilisticPsystemFactory, SpikingPsystemFactory, SymportAntiportPsystemFactory, TissueLikePsystemFactory, TransitionPsystemFactory, TSCSPsystemFactory

    public interface IPsystemFactory
    This interface is intended to be implemented by a P-system factory for each supported model. Each factory should be able to create its own CheckRule instances (which makes sure the p-system complies with the model conditions) and its own CreateSimulator, which should be able to create simulators for that model
